(January 28, 1954.)

Florence C. Barclay, on Behalf of Edgar L. Marston, III, Respondent, v. Edgar L. Marston, II, Appellant.

Order unanimously affirmed and the order of this court, entered January 26,1954, vacated. Present — Peek, P. J., Bastow. Botein and Bergan, JJ. [See ante, p. 658.]
